name: Showcasing American Cities
description: This image, "Showcasing American Cities" was created with the assistance of artificial intelligence (AI). The concept behind this image was to reflect on the beauty, landscapes, and diversity within America's cities. The process for creating this image included using a text prompt, algorithms, and artificial intelligence. The Snowpixel App was used in this process of creating this unique image. The image will be interpreted differently through the eyes and imagination of the viewer.
